      <hedline>
        <hl1>A Lyme Battle Rages</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Debbie Parret letter comments on May 23 article on controversy over treating Lyme disease</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The article ''Questioning Long-Term Lyme Cases'' (May 23) depicts Western medicine politics at its worst. The situation may seem bizarre to those who have not experienced the complications of Lyme disease but, as one who has, I can state that there are many more patient stories similar to those in the article.</p>
        <p>DEBBIE PARRETT  Centerville, Ohio</p>
      </block>
